strings: <voice_0x01001CBF><se_high>Media princess: I really appreciate our time together <hero>
<voice_0x01001CC0><se_high>Media princess: We know how dangerous predator fights can be. I know you risk your life for us.
<voice_0x01001CC1><se_high>Media princess: This may be your last chance to speak before the battle starts <hero>.
<voice_0x01001CC2><se_high>Media princess: please do not give up
<voice_0x01001CC3><se_high>Media princess: the whole world is with you
<voice_0x01001CC4><se_high>Media princess: But I'm glad that our destiny is in your hands...
